frames.caption: A whimsical scene depicts miniature people interacting with a tower of latte cups. A hand is seen pouring coffee into the top cup, while tiny figures appear to be working and climbing around the cups. The intricate latte art adds an artistic touch to the playful setup.
frames.description: The scene is set in a creative and imaginative environment where miniature people are engaged in activities around a pyramid of latte cups. The focus is on the interaction between the tiny figures and the oversized cups, creating a surreal and playful atmosphere.

frames.caption: A whimsical scene depicts a tower of coffee cups being filled with espresso, with miniature figures seemingly working on the cups. The figures appear to be baristas, adding a playful and imaginative element to the scene.
frames.description: The image captures a creative and surreal setting where a stack of coffee cups is being filled with espresso. Miniature figures resembling baristas are interacting with the cups, adding to the fantasy-like atmosphere.
